    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="📅-Overview"><a href="#📅-Overview" class="headerlink" title="📅 Overview"></a>📅 Overview</h2><p><strong>Date:</strong> 2025年12月28日 - 2026年1月14日<br><strong>Route:</strong> 东京 → 京都 → 大阪 → 札幌 → 洞爷湖 → 函馆 → 札幌</p><ul><li>✈️ <strong>JFK → Tokyo HND</strong>: ANA airline (Dec 27 1305 - Dec 28 1740)</li><li>🚄 <strong>Tokyo → Kyoto</strong>: Shinkansen 新干线 (Jan 1 0921 - 1132)</li><li>🚄 <strong>Kyoto → Osaka</strong>: JR (Jan 4)</li><li>✈️ <strong>Osaka ITM → Sapporo CTS</strong>: JAL airline (Jan 4)</li><li>🚌 <strong>Sapporo ↔ Lake Toya</strong>: Bus (Jan 9)</li><li>🚄 <strong>Lake Toya → Hakodate</strong>: JR (Jan 9)</li><li>🚄 <strong>Hakodate → Sapporo</strong>: JR (Jan 10)</li><li>✈️ <strong>Sapporo CTS → Shanghai PVG</strong>: 新千歳空港 13:50 → 浦东T2 (Jan 14)</li></ul><h2 id="🗓️-Itinerary"><a href="#🗓️-Itinerary" class="headerlink" title="🗓️ Itinerary"></a>🗓️ Itinerary</h2><h3 id="Tokyo"><a href="#Tokyo" class="headerlink" title="Tokyo"></a>Tokyo</h3><details close><summary>Day 1-4: Tokyo 东京 (Dec 28-31)</summary>Overview  <p><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/tokyo-00.png" alt="tokyo"></p><p>Dec.29</p><p><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/tokyo-01.png" alt="tokyo"></p><p>Dec.30</p><p><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/tokyo-02.png" alt="tokyo"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/tokyo-02-meiji.png" alt="tokyo"></p><p>Dec.31 (New year’s eve)<br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/tokyo-03.png" alt="tokyo"></p></details><p><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_1892.JPG" alt="tokyo sumida"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_1905.JPG" alt="tokyo sumida"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_1910.JPG" alt="tokyo shibuya"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_1911.JPG" alt="tokyo shibuya"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_1931.JPG" alt="tokyo koto"></p><hr><h3 id="Kyoto"><a href="#Kyoto" class="headerlink" title="Kyoto"></a>Kyoto</h3><details close><summary>Day 5-8: Kyoto 京都 (Jan 1-4)</summary><p>Overview</p><p><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/kyoto-00.png" alt="kyoto"></p><p>Jan.2</p><p><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/kyoto-01.png" alt="kyoto"></p><p>Jan.3  </p><p><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/kyoto-02.png" alt="kyoto"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/kyoto-03.png" alt="kyoto"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/kyoto-04.png" alt="kyoto"></p><p>Jan.4 (checkout - 从岚山回来去大阪)</p><p><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/kyoto-05.png" alt="kyoto"></p></details><p><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_1957.JPG" alt="kyoto"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_1963.JPG" alt="kyoto"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_1965.JPG" alt="kyoto"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_1966.JPG" alt="kyoto"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_1974.JPG" alt="kyoto"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_1975.JPG" alt="kyoto"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_1980.JPG" alt="kyoto"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_1981.JPG" alt="kyoto"></p><p><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_1983.JPG" alt="Otsu"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_1986.JPG" alt="Otsu"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_1991.JPG" alt="Otsu"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_1992.JPG" alt="Otsu"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_1995.JPG" alt="Otsu"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_1997.JPG" alt="Otsu"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_1998.JPG" alt="Otsu"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_2001.JPG" alt="Otsu"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_2003.JPG" alt="Otsu"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_2008.JPG" alt="Otsu"></p><hr><h3 id="Hokkaido"><a href="#Hokkaido" class="headerlink" title="Hokkaido"></a>Hokkaido</h3><details close><summary>Day 9-18: Sapporo 札幌 (Jan 5-14)</summary><p>Overview<br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/hokkaido-00.png" alt="hokkaido"></p><p>Jan.6</p><p><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/hokkaido-01.png" alt="hokkaido"></p><p>Jan.7-8<br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/hokkaido-02.png" alt="hokkaido"></p><p>Jan. 10<br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/hokkaido-03.png" alt="hokkaido"></p><p>Jan. 11-14<br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/hokkaido-04.png" alt="hokkaido"></p></details><p><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_2097.JPG" alt="Sapporo"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_2108.JPG" alt="Sapporo"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_2110.JPG" alt="Sapporo"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_2111.JPG" alt="Sapporo"></p><p><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_2044.JPG" alt="Toyako"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_2046.JPG" alt="Toyako"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_2047.JPG" alt="Toyako"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_2048.JPG" alt="Toyako"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_2052.JPG" alt="Toyako"></p><p><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_2057.JPG" alt="Hakodate"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_2061.JPG" alt="Hakodate"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_2062.JPG" alt="Hakodate"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_2067.JPG" alt="Hakodate"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_2069.JPG" alt="Hakodate"><br><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_2070.JPG" alt="Hakodate"></p><p><img src="/../images/travel/tokyo-kyoto-hokkaido/IMG_2077.JPG" alt="Otaru"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
